context.description:
This flow element helps you to trigger the deletion of messages in the data store. It enables you to specify ID(s) to be deleted in the Entry ID or pass them as header.
Note - ID(s) for deletion can also be read from message body by using Xpath expression. Xpath expression should return a node or node list. For example, ${xpath./n0:FSNMessageBulk/FSNMessage/RelatedMessageId/text()}
From the context menu of this element, you can also switch to other operations like: 1. Select 2. Get 3. Write
